{"tid":597664,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"史上最勵志大陸女團Sunshine翻拍日劇","createTime":"2018-03-19T00:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T08:53:02.000Z","uid":175614,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5409b8f9b7c0d1a64994d07f3043622701ec323e","tid":597664,"uid":175614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T00:04:14.000Z","msg":"日劇《人 100% 靠外表》由桐谷美玲擔任女主角，和水川麻美以及火紅諧星 Blouson 智惠美一起主演，3 人飾演在化妝品公司進行研發的「理工女」，由於整天都待在研究室而不善打扮、完全沒有異性緣，桐谷美玲將一步步進行「敗犬女」的改造。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/075553_c257e0b15f2f311a0652a9f5513f652a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F075553_c257e0b15f2f311a0652a9f5513f652a.png&h=50a1ab11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本海報<br />\n中國版的《人 100% 靠外表》，飾演桐谷美玲的女主角則是由 &nbsp;Sunshine 組合的團員 Cindy 擔任，中國微博上立刻瘋傳這個消息，並貼出了 Cindy 奇妙的日常生活照。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/075647_4fcd6dbbc870c33e901f5462afe728d0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F075647_4fcd6dbbc870c33e901f5462afe728d0.png&h=6805773e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCindy生活照<br />\n《人 100% 靠外表》由 &nbsp;Sunshine 組合的團員 Cindy 飾演女主角，職業為時尚髮型師的男主角，則是由年僅 20 歲的帥氣男星何德瑞擔任。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/075914_12d50b8d05ff97b589c5dcadd40a649e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F075914_12d50b8d05ff97b589c5dcadd40a649e.png&h=68868e40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男女主角合照<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/075947_2aa9fff0e1c9e290a563fe614df0a0ec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F075947_2aa9fff0e1c9e290a563fe614df0a0ec.png&h=e6002482&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本版男女主角合照<br />\n另外女主角身邊的兩名同事女配角，也將由 Sunshine 組合的團員Abby和Dora（前Sunshine組合拆夥後另組女團3unshine）飾演，簡直是為了這一個中國偶像女團而製作的連續劇。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/080132_3f8ae661de91dd930df9deb2af06dcbb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F080132_3f8ae661de91dd930df9deb2af06dcbb.png&h=1be4ef72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/080210_027b4f31323107d230a1a9912226fc6e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F080210_027b4f31323107d230a1a9912226fc6e.png&h=7c34871e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAbby與Dora照片"},{"pid":"104f7ea1450f55df3d65dd4a669d7414b34421a3","tid":597664,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T00:07:55.000Z","msg":"cindy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53598e7fcaa432ffd0e4c51c165c622db242af93","tid":597664,"uid":49588,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T00:10:38.000Z","msg":"好有中國地獄鬼國特色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a971c6d4835ca36293ea3209dd5c8db1b21f4e","tid":597664,"uid":116704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T01:09:58.000Z","msg":"嘩⋯邊個會睇"},{"pid":"0632c1115a68d231eb6665993fa6ad69a9d99655","tid":597664,"uid":139815,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T01:11:32.000Z","msg":"Sunshine本身都係行日系,拍日劇都幾似"},{"pid":"bff30c1a3c7a47deeda2fdb738addcc88fc5a3db","tid":597664,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T01:21:10.000Z","msg":"Cindy點睇都似ブルゾンちえみ多啲喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f0687fcbfe2ae59cce5102c7a712982278fc7ab","tid":597664,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s